==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Nepalese
<hw>Nep`a*lese"</hw> <pr>(? ⟦or⟧ ?)</pr>, <pos>prop. a.</pos> <def>Of or
pertaining to Nepal, a kingdom North of India; <as>as, <ex>Nepalese</ex>
troops massed at the border</as>.</def> <altsp>[Formerly written
<asp>Nepaulese</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> Nepali.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Nepalese</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Nepalese
<hw>Nep`a*lese"</hw> <pr>(? ⟦or⟧ ?)</pr>, <pos>prop. n. sing. &
pl.</pos> <def>A native or natives of Nepal, or an inhabitant of
Nepal.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Nepali</ent>⟦br⟧
